## Name of the node — use long name with explicit IP to avoid hostname resolution issues
-name pluto@127.0.0.1

## Cookie for distributed erlang (not used in v1, but set for safety)
-setcookie pluto_secret

## Enable heart for crash recovery
## -heart

## Increase process limit
+P 1048576

## Increase port limit
+Q 65536

## Enable SMP
-smp auto
